title: Irene C. Dominguez
maintext:
Irene C. Dominguez, 83, passed away on Friday, November 25, 2016 at a local hospital.
Funeral services were held on Saturday, December 3, 2016 departing from the Hernandez, Lopez and Sons Northside Chapels, 800 Boston St. on San Bernardo Ave.
Holy Mass was celebrated at San Luis Rey Catholic Church.
Committal services and interment followed at the Calvary Catholic Cemetery.
Pallbearers were Larry Rodriguez, John Avila, Juan R. Garza, Esau Huerta, Jesus Gonzalez Jr. and Raul Alfonso Lugo.
www.HernandezLopezFH.com.
